{"tid":1816474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（成績表）旅行團來港跌幅達9成 料支那客數字續偏低","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T09:46:05.000Z","uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8decdb3a353c12c98f275750a571bec9900bddc","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"黃進達指旅行團來港跌幅達9成　料內地客數字續偏低<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會主席黃進達說，<span style=\"color: red;\">旅行團來港數字持續低落，達到9成的跌幅，本月的情況都未有大改善，預計農曆新年或之後的內地旅客訪港數字將維持在較低水平</span>，海外市場同樣沒大改善。他說，近期示威活動相較不太激烈，社會氣氛較緩和，加上酒店價格下跌3成，以及各種零售優惠等，希望可吸引更多旅客來港。另外，對於財政預算案的期望，黃進達相信派錢有幫助，但認為刺激消費、令香港整體環境平穩，才能令業界有信心。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-08 16:47:17 RTHK"},{"pid":"3d72187ddf09c83cd7371e43185e6472169dcebc","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"國泰贊助免費入場嘅西九嘉年華，大家去唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f611f0e5fe498df20c1fb7eca3288f52d91e0a","tid":1816474,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:13:08.000Z","msg":"康泰仔？"},{"pid":"9d6841f491ff0dcfdfdf8f48653d21d70f466e48","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"仲有唔少自由行，大家唔好自滿"},{"pid":"a924bf6855709316273e2fa4a647543505630a0e","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418828422357ade6109465c6430320f6bf28f40e","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b7e6cfcac9e8d0ad4cb8dd9ee74cc01ff8da4a","tid":1816474,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c